column2: SELECT up_id,  dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) as SpecobjId   FROM #upload  WHERE  dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) IS NOT NULL  SELECT TOP #   s.ra,s.dec,cast(str(s.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,cast(str(s.[dec],#,#) as float) as dec  FROM ..SpecObj as s  JOIN #x AS x ON x.SpecobjID=s.SpecobjID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  s.zWarning = #   ORDER BY x.up_id
